word_mean_info__list.difference: 指尽管作出完全让步，也不会发生任何影响。
口语常用词，语气较强，泛指与前述情况相反。
表转折关系，语气稍弱于but，连接性也弱一些，因而常作插入语。
语气强，多用于肯定句或疑问句。指尽管作出让步，采取措施或表示反对，但情况仍然如故，无所改变。
表对比，一般可与whereas换用，但程度弱一些。
常用于否定句，语气比still稍强。指不管作出多大努力或让步，仍达不到预期的结果。
指过去已经开始的动作，说话时仍在继续，可用于肯定、否定或疑问句中。
通常用于疑问句和否定句中，指预料要发生的事，但尚未发生。

bilingual.source: The title is yet to be announced.
Man has not discovered any life in space yet.
bilingual.target: 人类尚未在太空中发现任何生命。

bilingual.source: The case of the Iceman isn't closed yet and investigations will continue.
bilingual.target: 冰人的案件尚未结案，调查将继续进行。

bilingual.source: The effect of the new policy has yet to be seen.
bilingual.target: 新政策的效力尚未显现。

bilingual.source: The source of infection for this outbreak has not been identified yet.
bilingual.target: 这次疫情的传染源尚未确定。

bilingual.source: The putative heir to the throne has not yet been officially named.
bilingual.target: 王位的假定的继承人尚未正式命名。

bilingual.source: The Minoan script, known as Linear A, has not yet been deciphered.
bilingual.target: 米诺斯文字，称为线性文字A，尚未被破译。

bilingual.source: The idea of traveling through time is conceivable but not yet proven.
bilingual.target: 穿越时间的想法是可想象的，但尚未被证明。

bilingual.source: The new treatment is unproven and not yet approved by the FDA.
bilingual.target: 这种新疗法是未经证实的，尚未得到FDA（食品药品监督管理局Food and Drug Administration）的批准。

bilingual.source: Its fate is yet to be decided.

list.abstract: Yet，英文单词，发音为/jet/（英）、/jɛt/（美），作副词、连词，翻译为还、但是、已经、而且等。

yingyinNormal.en: Because this world doesn't belong to you or the people who came before. It belongs to someone who has yet to come.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为这个世界并不属于你，也不属于之前来过的那些人，这里属于尚未到来的那个人。

yingyinNormal.en: Mrs. Underwood, the White House has yet to release one piece of information about the attempted capture of those domestic terrorists. ICO terrorists, yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 安德伍德夫人。白宫尚未发表任何关于抓捕那些国内恐怖分子的情况。哈里发国恐怖分子。是的。

yingyinNormal.en: Have you seen him yet? No, not yet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你见他了吗？还没。

yingyinNormal.en: Did you find him yet?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你找到他了？

yingyinNormal.en: Is Amanda here yet? No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 阿蔓达来了吗？还没。

yingyinNormal.en: You're on the porch yet?
yingyinNormal.zh: 到门口了没?

yingyinNormal.en: It's not over yet, you know.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还没结束呢，你知道的。

yingyinNormal.en: And yet. Voila! Bon appetite.
yingyinNormal.zh: 搞定啦。做好啦！祝您用餐愉快。

yingyinNormal.en: For what purpose? Don't know yet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 目的何在？还不知道。

yingyinNormal.en: And yet, you can't speak to women.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可你还是不敢和女人说话。

yingyinNormal.en: No. I didn't start yet. It's fine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不用了，我还没开始，所以没关系。

yingyinNormal.en: And yet, I know you know the truth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然而，我知道你们是了解真相的。

yingyinNormal.en: We do not yet know who violated us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们还不知道是谁袭击了我们。

yingyinNormal.en: We gotta hang on. Ned's not here yet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等下吧，内德还没来。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, Daddy, I haven't won a prize yet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，爸爸，我一个奖都没拿到。

yingyinNormal.en: Have you even talked to this guy yet?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你和他见过面了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Did you change yours to "Married" yet?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的状态改为"已婚"了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: No, let's not tell the mayor just yet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 先别告诉市长吧。

yingyinNormal.en: I thought you'd gone to bed. Can't yet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我还以为你已经睡了。还不能睡。

yingyinNormal.en: So any ideas for the bachelor party yet?
yingyinNormal.zh: 单身派对有想法了吗？

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 另一种；另一个；另外一个

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: in spite of the fact that

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Yet</highlight> as distrust has risen toward all media, people may be starting to beef up their media literacy skills.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，随着对所有媒体的不信任上升，人们可能开始提高他们的媒体素养技能。

examination_example.sentence: "Mass-produced clothing, like fast food, fills a hunger and need, <highlight>yet</highlight> is non-durable and wasteful," Cline argues.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Cline认为“大规模生产的服装，就像快餐一样，满足了人们的饥饿和需求，但却不耐用，还浪费”。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Yet</highlight> for the most part, the animal kingdom moves through the world downloading.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，对于大多数而言，动物王国通过世间的“下载”绵延发展。

examination_example.sentence: Mechanization isn't the answer, either – not <highlight>yet</highlight>, at least.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 机械化也不是答案——至少现在不是。

examination_example.sentence: Indeed, predictions have been around for two decades but have not <highlight>yet</highlight> come to fruition.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 事实上，预言已经存在了20年，但至今还没有实现。

examination_example.sentence: It is not <highlight>yet</highlight> clear how advertisers will respond.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 至今还不清楚广告商将如何回应。

sense_info_list.en: still; even(used to emphasize increase or repetition)

examination_example.sentence: How can the train operators possibly justify <highlight>yet</highlight> another increase to rail passenger fares?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 铁路运营商如何证明再次提高铁路客运票价是合理的？

word_usage.usage: yet用于否定句中表示某事尚未发生但有可能发生，如：They haven't finished yet 他们还没有完成。
yet在疑问句中用来询问某事是否已发生，如：Have you met my husband yet? 你见过我丈夫了吗？
yet作副词，可与and, but, although或though连用，如：a recent and yet more improbable theory 一个新近提出的但更加不切实际的理论。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: in spite of the fact that

examination_example.sentence: And if people aren't <highlight>yet</highlight> convinced by my arguments, I can give one final reason.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，如果人们还不相信我的论点，我可以给出最后一个理由。

examination_example.sentence: And <highlight>yet</highlight> despite how these employees feel, it's obviously important for their manager to nonetheless find out how to keep them motivated.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，不管这些员工的感受如何，对他们的经理来说，找到如何保持他们积极性的方法显然是重要的。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Yet</highlight>, when we speak of people from elsewhere, we seem to inevitably characterize them based on their country of origin.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，当我们谈到来自其他地方的人时，我们似乎不可避免地根据他们的原籍国来描述他们。

examination_example.sentence: While it has long been a practice in Asian countries, many people in Western countries have <highlight>yet</highlight> to embrace the no-shoes-in-the-house rule.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然这在亚洲国家早已成为惯例，但西方国家的许多人还没有接受“家里不穿鞋”的规定。

word_usage.usage: yet用于疑问句，通常放在句末。

yet与形容词或副词的比较级连用时意为“甚至，更”。
示例：a yet sadder tale
一个更悲伤的故事

yet与最高级连用意为“到目前为止（最…）”。
示例：It was the highest building yet constructed.
这是到迄今为止所建的最高的建筑物。

由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: in spite of the fact that

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Yet</highlight> numberless people struggle with tasks that require precise discrimination between quantities.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，无数人在与需要精确区分数量的任务作斗争。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Yet</highlight>, there are valid reasons boredom may feel so painful.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，无聊感如此痛苦是有充分理由的。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Yet</highlight> plenty has been lost too, even in cultures that still live to eat.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，即使在那些仍以饮食为生的文化中，也失去了很多。

examination_example.sentence: It may <highlight>yet</highlight> be a selection effect.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这可能还是一种选择效应。

examination_example.sentence: I've heard that German cars are very reliable, but I haven't decided on a specific model <highlight>yet</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我听说德系车很可靠，但我还没有决定具体的型号。

examination_example.sentence: Jonathan and I are thinking of renovating our sitting room, not the whole house, not <highlight>yet</highlight> anyway.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 乔纳森和我正在考虑翻新我们的客厅，而不是整栋房子，至少现在还没有。

word_usage.usage: yet用于疑问句，通常放在句末。

yet与形容词或副词的比较级连用时意为“甚至，更”。
示例：a yet sadder tale
一个更悲伤的故事

yet与最高级连用意为“到目前为止（最…）”。
示例：It was the highest building yet constructed.
这是到迄今为止所建的最高的建筑物。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

examination_example.sentence: Summer has not even started <highlight>yet</highlight>, but temperatures have reached 40 degrees centigrade in the past three days.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 夏天至今还没有开始，但是在过去的三天里气温已经达到了40摄氏度。

sense_info_list.en: in spite of the fact that

examination_example.sentence: And <highlight>yet</highlight> messengers of the coming disturbance are likely to be ignored.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，“骚乱将会发生”的信息可能会被忽视。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Yet</highlight> there is evidence suggesting that the trend is growing.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，有迹象表明，这一趋势正在加剧。

examination_example.sentence: It does not cost much, <highlight>yet</highlight> we can still learn a lot.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然它花费不多，但我们仍然可以学到很多东西。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Many places around the country can expect the coldest weather <highlight>yet</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 全国许多地方可能会出现迄今为止最冷的天气。

examination_example.sentence: But I'm not sure what kind of engineer I want to be <highlight>yet</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是，我至今还不确定自己想成为什么样的工程师。

examination_example.sentence: Many middle school students don't <highlight>yet</highlight> know what they want to do.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 许多中学生至今仍未知道他们想做什么。

sense_info_list.en: in spite of the fact that

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Yet</highlight> every day we make more and more rubbish.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，我们每天却制造越来越多的垃圾。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Yet</highlight> they are usually afraid to tell their parents or teachers about their problems.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，他们通常害怕告诉父母或老师关于他们的问题。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Yet</highlight> every year over one third of the food produced worldwide goes to waste!
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，每年全世界生产的食品有三分之一以上被浪费掉了！

sense_info_list.en: till; even (used to emphasize increase or repetition)

examination_example.sentence: She said, "Better <highlight>yet</highlight>, start today. "
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她说：“更好的是，从今天开始。”

examination_example.sentence: This is <highlight>yet</highlight> another success for Chang'e 4.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这是嫦娥四号又一次的成功。
